46, \"to\": 1057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though four women will represent the nation in South Korea, only three can be selected for the Olympics in Paris, with Bromley particularly keen to impress in what is her latest tournament since becoming a mother 14 months ago.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986928086966176, \"rank\": 0.0013088194871467525, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.887533053281772e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"score\": 0.6649350286297533, \"rank\": 0.5039061065322948, \"text\": \"Bromley\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four women\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"her latest tournament\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"a mother\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prospect of an Olympic call-up was considered a distant dream following the birth of her son, Lachie, but it's one the 36-year-old now hopes to use as proof that \\\"anything is possible\\\".\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prospect\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic call-up\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"a distant dream\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"the birth\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"her son\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"Lachie\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"proof\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think if you asked me when I was pregnant if I would continue playing at a high level, I was 90 per cent 'no',\\\" Bromley toldSBS Sport.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high level\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \",\\\" Bromley toldSBS Sport\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You just automatically think, 'oh, it's going to be too much for someone to take on; being a mum and trying to do sport as well'.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"a mum\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was still training two days a week while I was pregnant; just to keep in touch with the community, my feel on the ball, and things like that, and I kind of just snowballed from there.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two days\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought I would just use it as a bit of fitness to get back into shape, and then the next minute I was starting to compete again and actually not playing too bad.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, I thought I may as well go for it and try get another Olympics under my belt.\\\"\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another Olympics\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"my belt\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely been a learning curve but also fun at the same time,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a learning curve\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think what I would love to do is show people that your life before having a baby does not have to change too much.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would like to show people that anything is possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Balancing life as a parent with that of an athlete has been a \\\"fun process\\\" for Bromley, who also threw full-time work into the mix after recently returning from maternity leave.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"score\": 0.6649350286297533, \"rank\": 0.5039061065322948, \"text\": \"Bromley\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a parent\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"fun process\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time work\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"maternity leave\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, such commitments have not hindered her ability on the court, with tournaments like the World Team Championships the perfect opportunity to test herself on the international stage.\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber_Cup\", \"score\": 0.5564643999107509, \"rank\": 0.797060151844088, \"text\": \"World Team Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uber_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such commitments\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"her ability\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect opportunity\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most important thing for the Australian athletes is being able to have access to international match play,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2868, \"end\": 2878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.6987010689895599, \"rank\": 0.4299521676570035, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\"