ut I knew that if I stuck to being consistent with my training plan and working hard, I would see improvements in my game.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my training plan\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"improvements\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"my game\", \"from\": 4094, \"to\": 4101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, in the back of your mind, you do start getting niggles of thoughts saying, 'is the hard work actually ever going to pay off?'\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4134}, {\"ngram\": \"niggles\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"thoughts\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4176}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard work\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's all about staying strong in your belief in yourself, not worrying about what anyone else might be saying - or questioning - about your abilities.\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your belief\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"your abilities\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what I did; I just pushed the negative thoughts aside and kept pushing and pushing and driving that consistency and hard work into my training each day.\\\"\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the negative thoughts\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"that consistency\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"my training\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having carved a career from self-belief thus far, Bromley's remarkable return to Team Australia should come as no surprise as she knocks on the door to Paris.\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4605, \"end\": 4612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"score\": 0.6649350286297533, \"rank\": 0.5039061065322948, \"text\": \"Bromley\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bromley\"}, {\"begin\": 4636, \"end\": 4650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9996066481377592, \"rank\": 0.00039350664895224346, \"text\": \"Team Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 4707, \"end\": 4712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.887533053281772e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4577}, {\"ngram\": \"self-belief\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4594}, {\"ngram\": \"no surprise\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4677}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 4695, \"to\": 4703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if it is indeed the final item left on her list of achievements, it's one she will not be accomplishing alone.\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final item\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"her list\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4766}, {\"ngram\": \"achievements\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can qualify for Paris, that would be absolutely amazing,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 4831, \"to\": 4905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4853, \"end\": 4858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.887533053281772e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", 